Let there be a list called "leaps" that begins empty.

For every year from 2000 to 2050, do the following:
    If year is divisible by 400, remember year as leaps.
    Otherwise, if year is not divisible by 100, if year is divisible by 4, remember year as leaps.

Say "The leap years between 2000 and 2050, by the Gregorian rule:".
Print leaps, separated by ", ".
Say "How many of them in that span:".
Print the length of leaps.
